featureType.name: SeamapAus_NBHL_unvalidated
featureType.title: Seamap Australia National Benthic Habitat Layer - UNVALIDATED data
featureType.abstract:
The Seamap Australia UNVALIDATED National Benthic Habitat Layer is a collection of all candidate habitat datasets considered for inclusion in the Seamap Australia National Benthic Habitat Layer, but that have not been validated by ground-truthing seafloor observation (ie are exclusively modelled).
Note that this is an ancillary product to the Seamap Australia National Benthic Habitat Layer (NBHL) and DOES NOT meet the current standards required for inclusion in the NBHL.
